Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.60,0:01:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.73,0:01:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶带我去洗温泉 当做是情人节的回礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.81,0:01:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到大家的温柔对待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.07,0:01:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我度过了一个温暖快乐的幸福时光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.62,0:01:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,春天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.48,0:01:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人雀跃不已的新学期开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.89,0:01:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也都升为二年级了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.93,0:01:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一年级的新生都很可爱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.73,0:01:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹跟小鱼也来参加开学典礼就好了说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.83,0:02:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.97,0:02:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光是花粉的过敏就够受了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.81,0:02:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪还受得了一直待在那里呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.24,0:02:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 那王子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.88,0:02:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是开学典礼的干部 好像很忙的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.11,0:02:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真辛苦耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.58,0:02:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像很快就会受到一年级新生爱的攻势了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.39,0:02:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学长…我的学生手册好像弄丢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.29,0:02:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种事问我也没用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.33,0:02:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦 没有办法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.96,0:02:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还记得在哪里弄丢的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.70,0:02:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再去找找看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.43,0:02:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你先告诉我你的姓名与班级吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.54,0:02:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是有森佐登美 15岁 天蠍座 B型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.64,0:02:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喜欢手工艺 魅力在修长的脚踝..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.61,0:02:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是园宫里奈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.74,0:02:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家都说我像藤原静香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.38,0:02:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你个头啦 白痴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.71,0:02:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.28,0:02:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家羡慕的这一关 你冲得过去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.69,0:02:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.99,0:02:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年也许还会成为学生会长呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希好像不太喜欢这样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.73,0:03:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 我还在家长席上接收到疑似紫吴的电波呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.97,0:03:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对 他有来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.24,0:03:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为一年级里有草摩家的人入学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.91,0:03:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.51,0:03:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我来说他们就像我的弟弟一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.25,0:03:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我一定得出席一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.71,0:03:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看看他们光鲜亮丽的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.75,0:03:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么意思啊？用那种怀疑的眼神？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.06,0:03:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该不会是认为我是打女高中生的主意才去的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.36,0:03:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀 真讨厌耶 这群失去天真浪漫的小家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.70,0:03:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猪头…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.87,0:03:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有草摩家的人要入学呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.01,0:03:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.87,0:03:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么样的人？男的还是女的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.21,0:03:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男的 而且是两位呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？那去见他们一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.98,0:03:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 身为学长总得教一下学弟才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.02,0:04:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,例如这个学校的规矩、开溜之道等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 你去带他们过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 去带他们来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.76,0:04:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么是我 叫她去就好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.56,0:04:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种麻烦事干嘛非叫小透去才行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.87,0:04:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.07,0:04:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.54,0:04:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 我本来就打算去跟他们打声招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我去没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.91,0:04:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但难得嘛 阿夹要不要也一起去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.82,0:04:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托 为什么在学校还得见这些家伙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.89,0:04:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在学校见面搞不好感觉又不一样呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.06,0:04:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许别有一番滋味唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.33,0:04:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.46,0:04:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他好像愈来愈不能抗拒小透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.53,0:04:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.74,0:04:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶跟泼春是哪一班的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.71,0:04:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.64,0:04:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.68,0:05:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是够了 你在这里等 我去问一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？真的吗？不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.65,0:05:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你们知道有两个叫做草摩的白发跟金发的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道 就在我们班上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.16,0:05:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫他们过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.93,0:05:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 至少也搞清楚班级嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么总是迷迷糊糊的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.57,0:05:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你看那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.07,0:05:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个女孩挺可爱的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.04,0:05:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 是挺可爱的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.81,0:05:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是看起来有点呆耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.51,0:05:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那才好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.01,0:05:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不会反抗呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.44,0:05:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,个性强的女孩那才受不了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.88,0:05:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也对啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.88,0:05:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她看来好像还挺听话的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.15,0:05:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就叫她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.46,0:05:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可怕 可怕 好可怕喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.73,0:05:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看吧 就是迷迷糊糊的才会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.54,0:05:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个人的时候罩子要放亮点嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.04,0:06:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老是这样子 就算被绑架了也怪不了谁呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.21,0:06:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.14,0:06:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是说一个人的时候啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.78,0:06:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.88,0:06:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在身边的时候迷糊点是没有关系的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.75,0:06:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.19,0:06:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可没有别的意思喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.75,0:06:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别误会喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是想歪了 那可就头大了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.16,0:06:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？别的意思是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.80,0:06:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到底在说什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.80,0:06:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白痴呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.20,0:06:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是红叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.67,0:06:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.57,0:06:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.48,0:06:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是猪头呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.81,0:06:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹打我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白痴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.61,0:06:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么不好穿 哪有人穿女生制服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.85,0:06:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 冷静一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.18,0:06:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 是泼春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.65,0:06:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,屌儿啷当的泼春还好一点呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.22,0:06:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么关系 蛮速配的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.63,0:06:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很速配吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 很好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.43,0:06:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,问题不在这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.06,0:06:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托 你这什么打扮呀 红叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.81,0:07:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 工作结束了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.34,0:07:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.88,0:07:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到处巡视一下 顺道过来看看他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.41,0:07:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听我说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家叫我在学校不要太出风头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.99,0:07:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说要是太出风头的话就会受到女生的攻击呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.42,0:07:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我决定在学校要酷一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷吗？这种样子会酷吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.79,0:07:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说得好 2年D班的草摩夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.36,0:07:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那个橘子头也是很让人不爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.77,0:07:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男生却穿女生制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.54,0:07:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还真是空前绝后的厚颜无耻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.17,0:07:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算老师允许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.67,0:07:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也绝不原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.21,0:07:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我是这里的学生会长 竹井诚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.98,0:07:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有另一个头衔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.08,0:07:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是学校防卫队的队长！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.29,0:07:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又多了个白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.99,0:07:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才开学就是一堆问题学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.76,0:07:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先你这算什么 草摩泼春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点给我剥掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.43,0:08:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戴着满头白假发到处乱逛 你也太嚣张了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.07,0:08:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会长 他这是真的头发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.10,0:08:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇 由希～ 真是太美了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,言归正传 真发？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是下面的是黑的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.44,0:08:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是这是真发啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太不可思议了 怎么可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.08,0:08:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真伤脑筋 总不能说是牛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有你这打扮算什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.45,0:08:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道你也是与生俱来的吗？草摩红叶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.85,0:08:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你难道没有男性的尊严吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.42,0:08:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在就这样 我看你这辈子也不会有出息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.09,0:08:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 可是 这样比较适合我嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.63,0:08:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要太严厉的责骂他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可没责骂他喔 本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.77,0:08:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是基于常识在发表理所当然的言论而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.44,0:08:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少在那边装老大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.81,0:08:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实在很刺耳耶 你这个混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.65,0:08:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我倒是想问你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.38,0:08:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁说袜子折三次就是乖宝宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.82,0:09:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没穿耳洞就不会被欺负吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.19,0:09:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,头发不是黑的难道就犯法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.86,0:09:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以为你是谁啊？是神明吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.30,0:09:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"黑色降临"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你还真行呢 神明 说句话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.93,0:09:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫叫看呀 再啰唆呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会长…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了吧 别欺负外行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.70,0:09:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少啰唆！白痴猫 你不要插嘴！白痴猫！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.21,0:09:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准叫我白痴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.31,0:09:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要揍人了喔 臭小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.64,0:09:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？你跩什么跩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次打架时 是谁夹着尾巴逃跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.05,0:09:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是你自己不打的还说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.68,0:09:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙到底是那一边的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.42,0:09:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两边都一样 猪头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 要来颗糖吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.65,0:09:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,红叶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.82,0:09:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.89,0:09:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别找碴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.53,0:09:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你觉得怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.69,0:09:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算像红叶这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.19,0:09:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不觉得他在学校也不错吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.26,0:09:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正他迟早也会长大成人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要当男人 到那时候也不迟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.67,0:09:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定会变得很帅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.14,0:09:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光是想像红叶变成男人的样子 不是也挺有意思的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.04,0:09:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.87,0:09:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别被他洗脑了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.08,0:09:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是适合本人的打扮最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.81,0:09:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.85,0:10:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这根本就是任性妄为 对其他的学生也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.38,0:10:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也太失礼了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.95,0:10:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果由希也穿女生制服呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.02,0:10:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.86,0:10:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泼春 如果你不适可而止 我就跟你绝交了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.66,0:10:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说错话了 不可以生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.66,0:10:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定很棒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.83,0:10:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别乱想！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.43,0:10:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 我不知不觉的就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.77,0:10:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还真是个难缠的对手嘛 草摩泼春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.47,0:10:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.20,0:10:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你能证明你那头乱发是真发吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.11,0:10:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下…你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,证据确凿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这世界还真是无奇不有耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.97,0:10:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你给他看了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.50,0:10:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你给他看了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.51,0:10:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天算是我输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.27,0:11:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但下次可没这么简单喔 我会把你们一网打尽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.95,0:11:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些人到底是来干嘛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.28,0:11:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.92,0:11:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泼春 你在厕所是怎么证明你的头发给他看的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.36,0:11:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行呀 你要不要也和我试试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.66,0:11:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\an8\fs20}有没有洗手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.29,0:11:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.86,0:11:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一但变黑谁也拿他没办法…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.23,0:11:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.30,0:11:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 小透别放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\an8\fs20}蓦然地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.21,0:11:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然觉得好累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.67,0:11:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗 真的累了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 钟响了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.82,0:11:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得回教室去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.65,0:11:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去时要不要去见见我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.99,0:11:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的朋友？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.22,0:11:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊 我想见见小透的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.93,0:11:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.43,0:11:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那晚点我再来接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.36,0:11:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.57,0:12:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有话要跟由希、阿夹讲 你们可以等一下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.14,0:12:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.40,0:12:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我先回教室去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.51,0:12:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会 没那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.55,0:12:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.02,0:12:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是无聊事 我会扁人唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.46,0:12:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚真是大骚动一场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.63,0:12:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是如果以后每天都这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.73,0:12:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕由希跟阿夹都会很伤脑筋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.14,0:12:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像很快乐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.11,0:12:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说他来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.98,0:12:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说慊人来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.86,0:13:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们本来也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.18,0:13:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是刚刚在开学典礼时听紫吴说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.65,0:13:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是慊人自己突然说要来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.15,0:13:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我想他会比大家晚点到学校来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.99,0:13:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想先告诉你们一声比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.93,0:13:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怕你们不想见到他 所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.12,0:14:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是慊人…先生吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀 本田透小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.13,0:14:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次见面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.70,0:14:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是慊人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他怎么会来学校？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.10,0:14:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样子的见面方式可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.71,0:14:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吓了我一大跳 他好年轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.84,0:14:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且好漂亮 一点都不输给由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.05,0:14:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有他的眼神和波鸟…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.35,0:14:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很淑女 也挺温柔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.49,0:14:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来人蛮不错的 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.16,0:14:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最重要的是你很可爱喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.03,0:14:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 你过奖了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别紧张嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很可爱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.50,0:14:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在本家时没能与你打招呼 真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.94,0:14:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我是很怕生的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.71,0:14:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是否生气了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 哪会生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.95,0:15:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 那我再次自我介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.62,0:15:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是草摩家的大当家 慊人 请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.55,0:15:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 我也是…请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.52,0:15:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比我想像中的还平易近人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.90,0:15:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望今后能和你成为好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.90,0:15:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也请你多多关照由希他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.44,0:15:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慊人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.62,0:15:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.99,0:15:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好想你喔 由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.89,0:15:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感觉好久没见到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.63,0:15:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.70,0:15:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成熟了耶 也长高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.47,0:15:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你对小透做了什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.61,0:16:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是打声招呼而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.98,0:16:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不对 小透 只是打声招呼而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.02,0:16:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.22,0:16:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是由希 有件事情我一定要问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.99,0:16:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么过年时你没出席宴会？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.59,0:16:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么做这种事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.93,0:16:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近我对你也蛮宽大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.47,0:16:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你这样做实在太伤我的心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.21,0:16:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来我得再次教育你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.61,0:16:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那间你专用的房间…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.19,0:16:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么不听我的话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.67,0:17:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是草摩的大当家呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.94,0:17:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以为违背大当家会没事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.44,0:17:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要…不要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.29,0:17:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对…对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.83,0:17:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再不回教室…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会挨骂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.60,0:17:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.10,0:17:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.70,0:17:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是 再不回紫吴那边去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.71,0:17:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕他们也会担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.31,0:17:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 希望你有个愉快的高中生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.51,0:17:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若最近你愿意来找我 我会很高兴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.87,0:18:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我打断他们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.54,0:18:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希非常的害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.35,0:18:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.32,0:18:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慊人真的没对你说什么奇怪的事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.09,0:18:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有 真的只是打招呼而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.20,0:18:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 我们去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.56,0:18:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天学校比较早结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.80,0:18:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟小鱼他们说好了要去轻松一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.24,0:18:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正难得嘛 大家一起去玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.51,0:18:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实现在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.81,0:18:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想让由希受到慊人影响的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.82,0:19:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够快活起来罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.19,0:19:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有这件事情而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.09,0:19:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剪刀、石头、布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么要拖我下水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.36,0:19:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且还是羽毛球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.90,0:19:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是男人就别啰哩叭嗦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.17,0:19:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还带着口罩打呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.74,0:19:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也可以不要打呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.31,0:19:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分组之后呢？游戏规则呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.24,0:19:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么规则啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.41,0:19:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.11,0:19:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羽毛球不需要规则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用尽全力把球打出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.99,0:19:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再用力回打就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.45,0:19:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之 先倒的就是输家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.29,0:19:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不错 简单明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.26,0:19:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太简单明了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.33,0:19:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很啰唆耶 快到自己的阵地去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.47,0:19:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阵地？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.77,0:19:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是阵营
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.93,0:19:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧 王子 好好修理那个橘子头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.60,0:19:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么 太妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.41,0:19:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.38,0:19:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说小透…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.95,0:20:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不过是个丑八怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在回程的车上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.69,0:20:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是个丑八怪 真烂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.49,0:20:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来又不怎么聪明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.06,0:20:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是这种程度的女人的话 我就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.10,0:20:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想由希也撑不了多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.97,0:20:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反抗我的人是不会得到幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.27,0:20:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希现在见到我还是会害怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.81,0:20:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就表示他还没忘记我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.01,0:20:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,长期以来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.25,0:20:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,精神上受到那样的虐待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多少也有一些无法忘掉的伤痛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.56,0:20:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是慊人不会明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.53,0:20:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伤害别人的人也会受到伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.70,0:20:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这份创伤在他们之间永远存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.27,0:20:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记伤痛需要很大的勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.37,0:21:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且呢 小透又很可爱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.81,0:21:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人长的很甜美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.75,0:21:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这话由你说来感觉有点犯罪的意味喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.79,0:21:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有很想得到的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,描绘在内心的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.83,0:21:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥抱我的双亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.83,0:21:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以回去的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.20,0:21:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家可以尽情欢笑的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.67,0:21:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会被大家抛弃的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.48,0:21:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,温暖的归属
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.88,0:21:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,温馨的一群人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.29,0:21:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来真的存在

